# 🏋️ FitTrack - Workout Tracker

A full-stack workout tracking application built with Node.js, Express, React, and PostgreSQL.

## Features

- 🔐 User Authentication (JWT + bcrypt)
- 🏋️ Exercise Library (pre-populated)
- 📝 Log Workouts (sets, reps, weight)
- 📊 Dashboard Statistics
- 📜 Workout History
- 🔒 Protected Routes

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- Node.js + Express.js
- PostgreSQL
- JWT Authentication
- bcrypt for password hashing

### Frontend
- React.js
- Axios for API calls
- React Router for navigation
- React Toastify for notifications

## Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js v16+
- PostgreSQL v14+

### Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend
npm install
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your database credentials
createdb fittrack
psql -d fittrack -f ../database/ddl.sql
psql -d fittrack -f ../database/seed.sql
npm run dev